      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NO FIZZY DRINK (1) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (17.14) behind Freya Legend at this track. Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Likely to be in the finish again. VELVET LEGEND (8) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (23.15) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 6 over 395m. The form from her last run stacks up well. Can measure up. PEEPING PETE (4) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (31.59) at Angle Park. Should be about the money. JUST IS (6) cannot be ruled out.",
